titles.title: To designate the Federal building located at 300 East 8th Street in Austin, Texas, as the "J. J. 'Jake' Pickle Federal Building".

action.text: Referred to the House Committee on Transportation and Infrastructure.

bill.summary: 9/30/1996--Introduced. Designates the Federal building located at 300 East 8th Street in Austin, Texas, as the J.J. "Jake" Pickle Federal Building.
